== 網路爆紅 ==
{{Commonscat|Artwork_depicting_Natalia_Poklonskaya|娜塔莉亚·弗拉基米罗芙娜·波克隆斯卡娅衍生作品}}
波克隆斯卡娅出席了就職之後首次記者會、在大眾之前亮相後<ref>{{cite web |title=Crimean prosecutor Natalia Poklonskaya's viral video inspires fan art |url=http://www.cbc.ca/newsblogs/yourcommunity/2014/03/crimean-prosecutor-natalia-poklonskayas-viral-video-inspires-fan-art.html |publisher=[[CBC新聞|CBC News]] |accessdate=2014-03-21 |archive-date=2014-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141120002419/http://www.cbc.ca/newsblogs/yourcommunity/2014/03/crimean-prosecutor-natalia-poklonskayas-viral-video-inspires-fan-art.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因其清秀外貌而在[[互联网|網際網路]]上獲得廣泛矚目，[[人氣|人氣]]也因此快速攀升。波克隆斯卡娅的曝光還帶動了不少[[次元_(動漫用語)|二次元]]衍生作品，[[日本|日本]]社交网络出现大量以娜塔莉亚为藍本所創作的漫画，當中有許多是來自於[[艺术家|艺术家]]社群網[[pixiv|pixiv]]<ref>[http://kotaku.com/crimeas-attorney-general-spawns-anime-fan-art-1547001178 Crimea's Attorney General Spawns Anime Fan Art] {{Wayback|url=http://kotaku.com/crimeas-attorney-general-spawns-anime-fan-art-1547001178 |date=20210219125202 }}, Kotaku, 2014-03-19</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.j-cast.com/2014/03/20199816.html?igred=on |title=ロシア編入・クリミアの検事総長が「美人すぎ」！　ネットユーザー萌えまくり |publisher=J-CAST |date=2014-03-20 |accessdate=2014-03-26 |language=ja |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402111742/http://www.j-cast.com/2014/03/20199816.html?igred=on |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這些作品不僅引來[[俄罗斯之声|俄罗斯之声]]、[[今日俄罗斯|今日俄罗斯]]、[[俄罗斯报|俄罗斯报]]等俄國大型媒體的關注<ref name="voiceofrussia20140317" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://russian.rt.com/inotv/2014-03-19/YAponci-priznalis-v-lyubvi-prokuroru|title=Японцы признались в любви прокурору Крыма в стиле аниме|work=[[今日俄罗斯|今日俄罗斯]]|date=2013-03-19|language=ru|accessdate=2014-03-26|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214071411/https://russian.rt.com/inotv/2014-03-19/YAponci-priznalis-v-lyubvi-prokuroru|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rg.ru/2014/03/20/poklonskaya.html |title=Прокурор республики: Возглавить прокуратуру Крыма в эти дни испугались 4 мужчины. А она - согласилась |newspaper=[[俄罗斯报|Rossiyskaya Gazeta]] |date=2014-03-20 |language=ru |accessdate=2014-03-22 |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226092627/https://rg.ru/2014/03/20/poklonskaya.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC新聞]]和[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]等英美媒體也都加以報導<ref name=BBCart/><ref name=bloombergArt/><ref name="chinatimes"></ref>，而她本人在3月參加记者会的影片被上傳到[[YouTube|YouTube]]之後，一天之內就獲得30万次的点击<ref>{{cite news |title=Japan: Crimean attorney general inspires anime fan art |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/blogs-news-from-elsewhere-26663168 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=2014-03-20 |accessdate=2014-03-22 |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226092617/https://www.bbc.com/news/blogs-news-from-elsewhere-26663168 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=bloombergArt/>。

除了日本之外，波克隆斯卡娅也於[[中國|中國]]等地的網路[[网络名人|爆紅]]<ref name=IBTviral>{{cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/crimeas-attorney-general-natalia-poklonskaya-goes-viral-china-japan-1562620 |title=Crimea's attorney general Natalia Poklonskaya goes viral in China and Japan |publisher=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]] |date= |accessdate=2014-03-20 |archive-date=2020-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217153251/https://www.ibtimes.com/crimeas-attorney-general-natalia-poklonskaya-goes-viral-china-japan-1562620 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[中国新闻社|中国新闻社]]和[[光明日报|光明日报]]均對這位新檢察長製作了線上新聞<ref>{{cite web|title=克里米亚未婚美女检察长爆红 称“美丽挽救世界”|url=http://www.chinanews.com/tp/hd2011/2014/03-20/323133.shtml|publisher=[[中国新闻社|China News Service]]|accessdate=2014-03-21|archive-date=2020-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217153252/http://www.chinanews.com/tp/hd2011/2014/03-20/323133.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Newly appointed Crimean Gen.Prosecutor Natalia Poklonskaya draws Chinese netizens'attention |url=http://en.gmw.cn/2014-03/16/content_10686866.htm |publisher=[[光明日報|Guangming Online]] |accessdate=2014-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321081914/http://en.gmw.cn/2014-03/16/content_10686866.htm |archive-date=2014-03-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在中國的[[新浪微博|微博]]、[[美国|美国]]的[[4chan|4chan]]和[[Reddit|Reddit]]、以及[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]的[[VKontakte|VKontakte]]等[[社交網路服務|社交網路服務]][[網站|網站]]都激起了關於波克隆斯卡娅的熱烈議論<ref name=bloombergArt/>。

波克隆斯卡娅谈及自己的容貌时，表示：“有人会感到惊讶。我对我的外表道歉——似乎很清秀。但你们要知道，我从事[[司法|司法]]工作12年，我的容貌从来没有，将来也不会干扰我的工作。我向你保证”<ref>{{Cite news|title=克里米亞美女檢察長走紅網絡|url=http://la.stgloballink.com/global/2014/0321/79050.shtml|publisher=[[星島日報|星島日報]]洛杉磯版|date=2014-03-21|accessdate=2014-03-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325223627/http://la.stgloballink.com/global/2014/0321/79050.shtml|archivedate=2014-03-25}}</ref>。在接受中国[[环球时报|环球网]]记者专访时，她说：“我没时间上网，但‘美丽挽救世界’”<ref>{{cite web |url = http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2014-03/4916983.html |title = 独家专访克新任未婚总检察长：美丽挽救世界(图) |publisher = 环球网 |accessdate = 2014-03-20 |archive-date = 2018-07-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180713071100/http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2014-03/4916983.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

